  "detailed_description": "<h1>Joint development:</h1><p>Any interesting or abnormal suggestions can be fed back to us:<br>TikTok: 8959390uso</p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Multiple Role Playing</h2>Physical exorcism.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1727020/extras/d6e3b464fa4c54b885e4884508cd1a80.poster.avif?t=1690283808\" width=638 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1727020/extras/d6e3b464fa4c54b885e4884508cd1a80.webm?t=1690283808\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1727020/extras/d6e3b464fa4c54b885e4884508cd1a80.mp4?t=1690283808\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gun Enchanting</h2>A variety of magic free combination, strengthen the shooting effect of firearms.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1727020/extras/c6bb753c291dac26f8394708006bde94.poster.avif?t=1690283808\" width=638 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1727020/extras/c6bb753c291dac26f8394708006bde94.webm?t=1690283808\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1727020/extras/c6bb753c291dac26f8394708006bde94.mp4?t=1690283808\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1727020/extras/ca372be29cc2f9a5fc1788f93cd2ee7e.poster.avif?t=1690283808\" width=638 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1727020/extras/ca372be29cc2f9a5fc1788f93cd2ee7e.webm?t=1690283808\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1727020/extras/ca372be29cc2f9a5fc1788f93cd2ee7e.mp4?t=1690283808\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Data Architecture</h2>\"It adopts a numerical structure similar to WOW and Jianwang 3.<br>Supports long-term content updates (free).\"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Various scenes of land, sea and air</h2>\"With the development of the plot, players will experience the wonderful adventures of drifting, air combat, speeding cars, abyss, and missiles.<br>At the same time, each leader has playing skills, which require simple exploration and thinking.\"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Catch zombies as pets</h2>\"The ghouls you can see in the game can be caught and cultivated. After feeding fish, swallowing corpses, and sucking marrow, they can grow into reliable combat partners.<br>In addition, some renegade mercenaries and armored vehicles can also become your partners.\"<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1727020/extras/6c5825acfaefb4c0f7ce6086bc8dbaa0.poster.avif?t=1690283808\" width=638 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1727020/extras/6c5825acfaefb4c0f7ce6086bc8dbaa0.webm?t=1690283808\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1727020/extras/6c5825acfaefb4c0f7ce6086bc8dbaa0.mp4?t=1690283808\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Extraordinary gun weapons</h2>\"Cannons, muskets, stun guns, swords, axes, etc. will be updated in succession.<br>All are dropped by the world BOSS, and some duo copies are obtained.\"<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1727020/extras/3fbb1440dc16464c8de8460644f070fe.poster.avif?t=1690283808\" width=638 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1727020/extras/3fbb1440dc16464c8de8460644f070fe.webm?t=1690283808\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1727020/extras/3fbb1440dc16464c8de8460644f070fe.mp4?t=1690283808\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Other ways</h2>\"1. Fishing: Buy feed to lure the fish you want to catch, but it may also lure water ghosts to take the bait.<br>Fish can also be farmed, and they can grow very large.\"<br>2. Legion hegemony: Form a legion to compete for territory, and the legion that owns the territory can harvest rare coins every day.<br>3. Corpse battleground: conduct real-time PK and compete for the ladder ranking.",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Multiple Role Playing</h2>Physical exorcism.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1727020/extras/d6e3b464fa4c54b885e4884508cd1a80.poster.avif?t=1690283808\" width=638 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1727020/extras/d6e3b464fa4c54b885e4884508cd1a80.webm?t=1690283808\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1727020/extras/d6e3b464fa4c54b885e4884508cd1a80.mp4?t=1690283808\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gun Enchanting</h2>A variety of magic free combination, strengthen the shooting effect of firearms.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1727020/extras/c6bb753c291dac26f8394708006bde94.poster.avif?t=1690283808\" width=638 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1727020/extras/c6bb753c291dac26f8394708006bde94.webm?t=1690283808\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1727020/extras/c6bb753c291dac26f8394708006bde94.mp4?t=1690283808\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1727020/extras/ca372be29cc2f9a5fc1788f93cd2ee7e.poster.avif?t=1690283808\" width=638 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1727020/extras/ca372be29cc2f9a5fc1788f93cd2ee7e.webm?t=1690283808\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1727020/extras/ca372be29